item.content:encoded:
Rotating Rubiks Cube is an innovative Tetris game. It’s different from the traditional Tetris. You need to drop the given square vertically onto the rotating platform and support the platform to succeed. Successfully building a complete square frame can eliminate the score. Every landing square, the platform will be rotated. Do you want to challenge for high marks?
Use the mouse or your finger to play.

item.content:encoded:
The busy stickman opens his busy cycle of life again, lifts his briefcase and rushes to the next goal! In this game, you play a busy matchmaker, running crazily in the circle, avoiding obstacles carefully, and passing through the whole circle. How many passes can you get through? But notice that obstacles are not necessarily as quiet as you think.
Tap and hold to jump higher.

item.content:encoded:
Young ninjas hide in the fast-growing world of modern times and even drink juice is so cool. In Fruit Master, you need to throw a dagger and cut the fruit to squeeze the juice. The operation is extremely simple. Throw a dagger and cut the fruit. The fruit in the air is spinning so you may hit nothing. And the difficulty of the game will gradually increase. Can you become a fruit master? Come and have fun.
Use the mouse or your finger to play.

You are going to be the fruit ninja and cut up as many fruits as possible to win a high score. Don’t slice bombs or miss fruit.On PCDrag the mouse to cut.On mobileSlide the screen to […]
item.content:encoded:
Ninja Fruit Slice is a classic arcade game. The rule is simple, slice every fruit but not the bomb. You are going to be the fruit ninja and cut up as many fruits as possible to win a high score. Don’t slice bombs or miss fruit.
On PCDrag the mouse to cut.On mobileSlide the screen to cut.
